{"tid":505000,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"喺ig shop買野嘅人凈戇鳩!","createTime":"2017-12-20T16:04:00.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-02T15:25:43.000Z","uid":10345,"like":179,"dislike":31,"uniUserReply":48,"replies":[{"pid":"16729bf8639f435fbd90fc746a9513998dbc21da","tid":505000,"uid":10345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-20T16:04:00.000Z","msg":"明明無論連登定香討抑或yahoo問答有親IG shop比人呃既post都會比其他連登仔 or 香討ching屌 IG買野凈戇鳩! <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  比人坤抵死<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點解仲有人要上IG 買嘢咖!<br />\n<br />\n喺啦,又喺呢類post,小弟就係其中一個屢教不改既戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ,但我覺得其實IG shop買野識分真假其實都ok. 不如大家分享下有d咩技巧喺分得出係咪IG黑店呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 價錢 (stussy hoodies賣359? AJ x supreme hoodies賣599? 搞笑咩 咪貪小便宜啦)<br />\n2.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> Size (ultra boost 1.0 仲有齊碼? 男裝款有埋女款size? 成熟d啦)<br />\n3. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> follower (哇10k follower 入去睇 全部中東佬黎既 知咩事啦)<br />\n4.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其他..... 咩廠貨 絕對正版 台灣貨 知咩事啦,唔詳細講<br />\n5. <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 大家有冇d技巧去分,可以分享下,唔一定喺要喺ig shop買野架,拎黎分下黑店再笑下d 買野既戇鳩仔都好啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nbetween <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 今次小弟成為戇鳩仔同時都發現一個重點<br />\n可以睇下d post既留言,<strong>有時會show出黎有一個或幾個留言,但禁入去喺冇嘢既,咁咪即喺心有shit,留言del佐lor<br />\n</strong><br />\n講返重點!無論有冇人想知又好,比人鬧又好,我只喺想少d人成為水魚,受害者,錢多錢少都好,呃錢凈仆街!<br />\n<br />\n呢間鋪頭好多野好似好真咁,價錢又唔喺低得離譜wor,勝在款多,碼齊,事後問返d半個月前話好快cut order既單都齊碼有曬貨wor!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">店名: 24hoursjapanshop<br />\n電話: 66221168<br />\n銀行: 匯豐 634522478833 Y** H** H**&amp; C* S* W**<br />\n         中銀 01237510259967 C** S** W**</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/20/233316_dacfad0ca86ac0ec30befe55e3430fde.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2F233316_dacfad0ca86ac0ec30befe55e3430fde.png&h=14ee60ca&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n受害人圍爐IG: 24hoursjapanshopblackshop<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/20/234922_6b9f6da4a48645de9a66db3ceb4b1927.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2F234922_6b9f6da4a48645de9a66db3ceb4b1927.png&h=7c1da349&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n開佐半日已經有10個受害者穩,都有唔少證據或者花生喺個page度.<br />\n<br />\n咁呢間鋪頭點黑店法呢?<br />\n1.本人體驗,買三件,拖佐兩個月,當中寄過一件,但其實有d假貨feel,兩個月當中穩佢10次應該覆你一次,24horusjapanshop? 買完野24hours唔覆你機ja傻仔<br />\n2.其他受害人,有人試過報警,然後兇返黑店店主退款,依然不停拖之後成功<br />\n3.有人2個月內不停煩,終於收到貨,但明事理既潮童老公一睇就覺假,然後詢問話退完稅冇單證明邊度買(屌 淘寶都有稅退?)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/20/234322_c8c3c587266aa8f1d191b0d9343c544b.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2F234322_c8c3c587266aa8f1d191b0d9343c544b.PNG&h=fbc617ce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/20/234328_cd14a35686f4b6b795f9fc299da009d5.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2F234328_cd14a35686f4b6b795f9fc299da009d5.PNG&h=02a1cfa6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/20/234330_ad16874faa1ccbd27778ef235aed8f9e.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F20%2F234330